title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: Exception in: ReportEngineService.getMetaData() when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should result in the data being exported successfully.
SR:
To reproduce the bug:
1. Add a table to the report that includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Export the data from the table.
